<H2>Contacting Christian Zimmermann</H2></CENTER> 


You are most welcome to contact me with suggestions and criticism
regarding
my various websites, my research, my teaching or other matters. Due to the
volume of mail I receive, please
understand that I will not respond to irrelevant messages or messages
pertaining to stuff you can find for yourself on the web. I will for
example
not provide advice on current and future business conditions, I will not
compile for you a reading list or solve your take home exams.
<P>
My email address is <A
HREF=mailto:christian.zimmermann@uconn.edu>christian.zimmermann@uconn.edu</A>.
You may reach me by phone at (860) 486-3272, but I
strongly prefer email. My fax number is (860) 486-4463. For postal mail,
my address is:
<P>
Department of Economics<BR>
University of Connecticut<BR>
341 Mansfield Road, Unit 1063<BR>
Storrs, CT 06269 USA
 <P>

To see me in person, I am in office 318 of the Monteith Building. My office hours are Wednesday 8-12am.
<P>
To learn more about me and my projects, check out my <A
HREF=http://ideas.repec.org/zimm/>home page</A>.

